description: PROPOSED REVISIONS TO PLANNING PERMISSIONS REFS.10057/APP/2005/1620, 10057/APP/2007/1993 AND 1994, FOR THE COMPREHENSIVE REDEVELOPMENT OF THE FORMER HAYES & HARLINGTON STATION GOODS YARD SITE. REVISIONS TO INCLUDE: ALTERATIONS TO THE INTERNAL LAYOUT/ARRANGEMENT OF BUILDINGS B, C AND D; INTERNAL ALTERATIONS TO BUILDING E TO PROVIDE 16 FOUR-BEDROOM RESIDENTIAL UNITS (COLLECTIVELY INCREASING THE NUMBER OF RESIDENTIAL UNITS TO 576); AND INTERNAL CHANGES AT PODIUM LEVEL TO THE APART-HOTEL (BUILDING F) TO INCREASE THE NUMBER OF APART-HOTEL APARTMENTS TO 140 (DUPLICATE APPLICATION).
